         <td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt;" background="/images/bg_heading_blue_01.jpg"><center><b>The Legion of Light is recruiting 35+</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
		 <td>                            
	                                   

	    <table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
		  <tr><td><font color="00dd00">Submitted by:</td><td><font color="00dd00">Glamdering Foe'Hammer</td></tr>
        </table>
	  <br>
	  <br>


          Hello Noble Lords and Great Ladies<br>
          <br>
          I, Glamdering Foe'Hammer, post this to announce that the Legion of Light is looking for some higher levels to fill out our upper ranks and thus create an evenly distributed guild. <br>
          <br>
          We currently have over five level 50+s and around ten+ lvl 40+s, as well as a number of valued members below level 40.   However, we still desire more people for a closer knit, more group friendly guild!<br>
          <br>
          Some Info about us:<br>
          <br>
          I founded the The Legion of Light over a year and a half ago on August 1st 1999. At that time we were solely an Age of Kings guild.  Since that time the guild has grown and prospered.  When I discovered Everquest I was hooked and eventually founded our Everquest Division.  The Everquest Divison is now over 6 months old and both are doing well.  Below I have enclosed our charter, as I feel it best describes our focus.<br>
          <br>
          ~We, of the Legion of Light are sworn to valor. Our hearts know only virtue. Our blades defend the helpless and our might upholds the weak. Our words speak only truth and our wrath undoes the wicked that creeps throughout the land. Norrath is our home. We are explorers, adventurers, hunting companions, questors, traders, tutors, and artisans. Our pleasure comes from championing the Light, stretching our abilities, sharing with others, laughing, and having fun. We are a diverse group and in that lies our strength. We are bound by a code of honor, good sportsmanship, strength of arms, teamwork, and loyalty. Join us.~  <br>
          <br>
          You can visit us at http://www.thelegionoflight.cjb.net please make sure to click on the "Everquest" Division from the gateway page.  We also have several unique downloads to Everquest.<br>
          <br>
          Also feel free to contact me, Glamdering, or one of our other officers: Terria, Wrinkles or Catan.  Please make sure to mention that you seek to join and are coming from the Prexus.com Post.<br>
          <br>
          You may also contact me at the_ageless_dark_phoenix@yahoo.com<br>
          <br>
          -Walk in the Light-<br>
          -Glamdering<br>
          <br>
          <br>
          </td>
